<chapter id="jdiameter">

	<title>&THIS.PLATFORM;</title>

	<para>
		The Diameter Stack is basic component of diameter solution. It
		performs all necessary tasks to allow user interact with
		Diameter network. It manages state of diameter peers and allows to route
		messages between them. For details please refer to
		<ulink url="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3588">RFC 3588</ulink>
	</para>
	<para>
	Currently stack supports following application sessions:
	</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem>
			<para>Sh</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Ro</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Rf</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Cx</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>Dx</para>
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<para>CCA</para>
		</listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
	

